dct_title_s: Special war map of China, Korea, and Japan
dct_alternative_sm: Special War Map of China, Korea and Japan Compiled from the most Recent and Authentic Sources
dct_description_sm: Legend includes railways (open, constructing, and surveyed), treaty ports, submarine cables, roads, engagements.
Inset map of Port Arthur shows various buildings and facilities.
Engagements at Yalu River, Port Arthur, Wei-hai-wei.
Shows waterways, Great wall, "barrier of stakes," cities and towns, old bed and mouth of Yellow River.
